# Summary
Amplitude Activation's Meta Pixel streaming integration enables forwarding Amplitude events to Meta Pixel, requiring Meta Pixel ID and Conversions API Access Token for setup. The integration supports mapping Amplitude user properties to Meta Pixel Customer Information Parameters and sending additional properties as Custom Data Parameters.

